Wow! This is a great recipe. I also added zucchini to the kebabs. I think it would have been a little light on substance without it. I thought shrimp would make a nice addition, but that was a mistake; the swordfish was so tender and delicious and paired so well with the bacon... No sense mixing mediocrity with greatness! Next time I'll use only swordfish. An excellent recipe!

